flowchart TD
    A([Employee status changed in Directory]) --> B{New employee status}
    B -- Disabled --> C[Access user becomes DISABLED]
    B -- Archived/Terminated --> D[Access user becomes ARCHIVED]
    C --> E[All sessions revoked]
    D --> E
    D --> F[Pending invitation revoked]
    E --> G[User's next request is rejected]
    F --> G
    G --> H([User can no longer access HRMS])
